VALUES (@p0, @p1, @p2, @p3, @p4, @p5, @p6, @p7, @p8, @p9, @p10, @p11, @p12, @p13, @p14, @p15);
SELECT [Id]
FROM [AbpAuditLogs]
WHERE @@ROWCOUNT = 1 AND [Id] = scope_identity();
